description:         Combinator-based type-safe formatting (like printf() or FORMAT), modelled from the HoleyMonoids package.
license:             BSD3
license-file:        LICENSE
author:              Chris Done, Shachaf Ben-Kiki, Martijn van Steenbergen, Mike Meyer
